                        <li class="safety-tip flex items-start gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-600 mt-0.5"></i> <span>For electrical issues, switch off main power supply from the meter box</span></li>
                        <li class="safety-tip flex items-start gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-600 mt-0.5"></i> <span>Keep emergency numbers saved in your phone contacts</span></li>
                        <li class="safety-tip flex items-start gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-600 mt-0.5"></i> <span>Don't attempt DIY repairs for major electrical or gas emergencies</span></li>
                        <li class="safety-tip flex items-start gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-600 mt-0.5"></i> <span>Keep a fire extinguisher and first aid kit accessible</span></li>
                    </ul>
                    
