                <i class="fab fa-twitter text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 cursor-pointer transition text-xl"></i>
                <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 cursor-pointer transition text-xl"></i>
                <i class="fab fa-instagram text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 cursor-pointer transition text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">© 2025 Propbandhu | 24/7 Emergency Support for Property Emergencies</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-2">Trained professionals | Rapid response | Verified service providers</p>
        </div>
